-- Calgon Carbon Swings to Profit on Water, Activated Carbon Demand
-- B y   R a n d a l l   H a c k l e y
-- 2013-11-05T18:02:46Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-11-05/calgon-carbon-swings-to-profit-on-water-activated-carbon-demand.html
Calgon Carbon Corp. (CCC) , an activated
carbon and ultraviolet technology provider to clean water and
air, swung to a third-quarter profit from a year ago on demand
in the environmental water, food and specialty carbon markets.  Net income was $11.9 million compared with a $4.5 million
loss for the year-earlier period, the Pittsburgh-based company
said today in a statement. Sales rose 2.9 percent.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Randall Hackley in London at 
